The method should return a string `s`.
The string `s` should contain only the characters 'a' and 'b'.
The length of the string `s` should be equal to the sum of `a` and `b`.
The string `s` should not contain any consecutive 'a' characters.
The string `s` should not contain any consecutive 'b' characters.
The number of 'a' characters in the string `s` should be equal to `a`.
The number of 'b' characters in the string `s` should be equal to `b`.
The order of the characters in the string `s` should not matter.
The string `s` should be any valid string that satisfies the above conditions.
